WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.080 --> 01:42.920
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:54.600 --> 01:57.160
Amid power struggles among various forces,

01:57.240 --> 02:00.280
who would have thought
that Your Highness benefited the most?

02:01.560 --> 02:03.040
Upon a sea of corpses,

02:03.120 --> 02:05.600
you rose to glory.

02:06.640 --> 02:09.560
I really wonder whether General Chu
would feel relieved

02:10.600 --> 02:12.600
if he knew about it in the underworld.

02:13.200 --> 02:16.000
You don't need to bother
with my father's feelings.

02:18.240 --> 02:21.000
You invited me over again
after quite a few days.

02:21.080 --> 02:22.440
Will you not keep me as your guest?

02:23.920 --> 02:24.920
Originally,

02:25.000 --> 02:27.640
I wanted to ask you
to stay a few more days

02:27.720 --> 02:28.960
so that I could extend my hospitality,

02:29.560 --> 02:33.400
but now, our state can't do without you.

02:34.480 --> 02:35.840
That's true.

02:36.360 --> 02:38.520
Then thank you for your hospitality.

02:39.600 --> 02:43.520
Hope I'll have another chance to visit
the Prince of Xiaonan's Residence.

02:44.840 --> 02:46.720
Don't you remember, Your Highness?

02:49.880 --> 02:50.800
The court

02:51.800 --> 02:54.720
has titled me the Prince of State.

02:55.760 --> 02:57.920
I have got the Golden Seal

02:58.000 --> 02:59.600
and feudal sovereignty.

03:00.600 --> 03:02.520
So, "Prince of Xiaonan's Residence"

03:03.120 --> 03:05.560
will be "Prince of State's Residence".

03:06.400 --> 03:08.080
In this aspect,

03:08.800 --> 03:10.440
Xie Yanfang's plan

03:11.400 --> 03:13.760
coincided with yours.

03:14.560 --> 03:15.920
Interestingly enough,

03:16.000 --> 03:18.480
when Xie Yanfang was ten years old,

03:18.560 --> 03:21.280
his mastery of strategy was peerless.

03:21.360 --> 03:22.560
He deliberately lost 50 moves

03:23.240 --> 03:25.120
just for his final strike.

03:25.200 --> 03:26.320
With only a few pieces,

03:26.400 --> 03:29.640
he swept the board clean
against his mentor.

03:29.720 --> 03:31.560
That wondrous tale

03:31.640 --> 03:34.040
spread far and wide across the state.

03:34.720 --> 03:35.760
Oh, General Xie.

03:36.440 --> 03:38.320
Did you not tell Her Highness?

03:38.400 --> 03:40.680
Your brother's greatest skill

03:40.760 --> 03:45.080
is to make everyone think
he's the one in control of the game.

03:46.080 --> 03:48.320
It seemed like a fight between everyone.

03:48.400 --> 03:51.160
But actually, the Xie Family
manipulated the game.

03:51.240 --> 03:53.080
You're quite talkative today.

03:53.160 --> 03:54.480
Do you not want me to leave?

03:57.960 --> 03:59.280
General Xie,

03:59.360 --> 04:01.720
your brother is in the Capital,
and could it be--?

04:01.800 --> 04:02.760
I'm not a Xie.

04:03.920 --> 04:05.120
Nor do I have a brother.

04:06.360 --> 04:09.200
Oh, look at my poor memory.
I nearly forgot.

04:10.560 --> 04:11.800
Back then,

04:11.880 --> 04:14.720
you were even excluded
from the family genealogy.

04:15.320 --> 04:18.519
You two share the same father,
while he wielded power in Taiji Hall,

04:18.600 --> 04:20.959
and you led a primitive life
at the frontier.

04:21.040 --> 04:23.720
Totally different lives. How interesting.

04:23.800 --> 04:25.000
Mind your tongue.

04:31.160 --> 04:33.160
Don't be angry, Your Highness.

04:34.360 --> 04:35.720
I'm just curious.

04:35.800 --> 04:37.560
They're from the same family.

04:37.640 --> 04:40.840
Why did you not choose the one
who could help you more?

04:40.920 --> 04:43.440
After all, without the tacit cooperation
from Xie Yanfang,

04:43.520 --> 04:46.120
your schemes wouldn't have worked.

04:47.680 --> 04:49.080
That is none of your concern.

04:49.680 --> 04:52.240
I wish you good health.

04:53.400 --> 04:54.240
After all,

04:54.320 --> 04:58.000
it's not that easy to cultivate
a second Xiao Xun who can meet

04:58.080 --> 04:58.960
your standards.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.960
Jiu, let's go.

05:16.160 --> 05:17.240
You're right.

05:18.040 --> 05:19.560
I'm different from Xie Yanfang.

05:20.160 --> 05:21.520
I'm more resentful than him.

05:23.160 --> 05:25.360
So, hope you and your son

05:25.960 --> 05:27.720
will never end up in my hands.

05:32.960 --> 05:35.160
Come on. See Her Highness out.

05:35.240 --> 05:36.120
Yes.

05:46.040 --> 05:48.360
‎MILITARY CAMP OF CHU ZHAO’S TROOPS
‎IN XIAONAN PREFECTURE

05:49.760 --> 05:52.800
Are you so sure
the Lord of Xiaonan won't rebel?

05:53.720 --> 05:55.040
He wouldn't dare.

05:55.720 --> 05:57.600
Not now, at least.

05:57.680 --> 05:59.280
Back in his mansion,

06:01.600 --> 06:03.840
you said Xie Yanfang would make his move.

06:04.440 --> 06:05.680
You seem

06:07.200 --> 06:08.200
to know about everyone.

06:08.840 --> 06:10.080
I don't know.

06:10.600 --> 06:11.480
I plan ahead.

06:12.280 --> 06:13.600
Like in a Weiqi game,

06:13.680 --> 06:16.320
we need to foresee
the opponent's moves ten steps ahead.

06:16.920 --> 06:19.040
I simply foresee more steps ahead.

06:20.840 --> 06:21.800
He is right.

06:22.760 --> 06:23.640
What?

06:26.600 --> 06:27.720
Xie Yanfang and I

06:30.040 --> 06:31.160
are indeed different.

06:34.400 --> 06:35.440
And he can really…

06:39.920 --> 06:41.480
help you more.

06:42.440 --> 06:45.320
When I was seven,
I saw him for the first time.

06:46.080 --> 06:47.800
At the top of our ancestral hall.

06:48.840 --> 06:50.040
At that time,

06:50.560 --> 06:52.480
I began to imitate every move of his.

06:53.880 --> 06:55.240
I copied his speech and behavior,

06:56.560 --> 06:59.240
hoping that one day,
I could be as good as him.

06:59.880 --> 07:01.040
Even if…

07:04.600 --> 07:05.960
I could only be his shadow.

07:09.600 --> 07:10.480
Look at me.

07:13.640 --> 07:15.840
Remember. Jiu,

07:16.840 --> 07:18.840
you're no one's shadow.

07:19.760 --> 07:20.920
You don't need to be like him.

07:31.000 --> 07:32.720
But you praised him so highly.

07:35.120 --> 07:38.760
You firmly trusted every decision he made.

07:41.160 --> 07:44.080
Zhao, I know I shouldn't say this.

07:47.520 --> 07:48.680
I'm very jealous of him.

07:50.120 --> 07:51.360
I would even rather

07:52.440 --> 07:54.200
be his shadow again.

07:55.720 --> 07:56.840
Maybe then,

07:57.960 --> 07:59.680
I could help you more.

08:01.040 --> 08:02.160
Like I said,

08:02.840 --> 08:04.400
you're no one's shadow.

08:05.960 --> 08:07.040
You don't need to be like him.

08:08.920 --> 08:09.760
Whether Fu Jiu

08:10.600 --> 08:11.960
or Xie Yanlai,

08:13.080 --> 08:14.440
you're just what you are.

08:16.720 --> 08:18.000
What I am…

08:24.200 --> 08:25.440
I'm someone

08:26.240 --> 08:28.440
that no one expects anything from.

08:31.120 --> 08:32.200
Not even my parents.

08:33.400 --> 08:34.679
Your parents lied to you,

08:35.200 --> 08:36.840
but they actually loved you.

08:38.200 --> 08:39.280
My father hated me.

08:40.159 --> 08:41.400
My mother blamed me.

08:42.440 --> 08:43.840
Even my brother

08:46.080 --> 08:47.120
schemed against me.

08:47.960 --> 08:49.080
You still have me.

08:52.320 --> 08:53.760
Being betrayed by your own family

08:54.760 --> 08:56.200
must have broken your heart.

08:57.960 --> 09:00.000
But if you doubt the person
before you because of that,

09:00.520 --> 09:02.360
you'll fall right into their traps.

09:05.200 --> 09:06.040
I'm sorry.

09:18.200 --> 09:19.920
We love and trust each other.

09:21.040 --> 09:23.640
And we'll grow old together.

09:53.080 --> 09:54.120
Your Lordship,

09:54.680 --> 09:56.680
the Grand Princess has left the city.

09:57.760 --> 09:59.400
This woman is better

09:59.480 --> 10:01.840
at striking a nerve than her father.

10:02.520 --> 10:04.680
His Highness is held captive
in the side residence.

10:05.280 --> 10:06.320
But don't worry.

10:06.400 --> 10:08.760
We've sent men
to take care of him in private.

10:08.840 --> 10:11.160
Does Xun blame me?

10:11.880 --> 10:14.640
He will understand that you had no choice.

10:17.760 --> 10:19.640
My son has always been sensible.

10:20.600 --> 10:24.160
He knows that a son relies on his father,
and a father schemes for his son.

10:26.760 --> 10:28.520
Why do you think

10:29.400 --> 10:32.280
Xie Yanlai is willing
to be Chu Zhao's blade?

10:33.680 --> 10:35.320
Perhaps for fame and wealth.

10:36.520 --> 10:38.400
Or perhaps for…

10:39.400 --> 10:40.560
beauty?

10:44.080 --> 10:46.040
The court is in a state of flux.

10:46.920 --> 10:49.120
Xun is trapped in the Capital.

10:49.720 --> 10:50.960
Xie Yanfang

10:51.480 --> 10:53.920
and Deng Yi have their own ambitions.

10:54.720 --> 10:58.120
And there is the Grand Princess,
who lies in wait to strike.

10:58.960 --> 11:02.120
Now, it has become a complete stalemate.

11:02.960 --> 11:06.640
No matter what Xie Yanlai is after,

11:06.720 --> 11:08.360
I have a feeling

11:10.600 --> 11:11.960
that he will be the one

11:13.120 --> 11:14.560
to break the stalemate.

11:18.080 --> 11:19.320
What's on your mind?

11:20.720 --> 11:21.880
Father once said,

11:21.960 --> 11:23.200
beyond the battlefield,

11:23.720 --> 11:25.320
human hearts are the most complex.

11:25.920 --> 11:26.920
Scared?

11:28.120 --> 11:29.600
I just think it's absurd.

11:31.320 --> 11:32.920
The Lord of Xiaonan wants fame.

11:33.000 --> 11:34.400
Xie Yanfang wants power.

11:34.480 --> 11:35.560
Deng Yi wants wealth.

11:36.080 --> 11:37.600
They never stop fighting.

11:37.680 --> 11:40.120
But no one has asked what our people want.

11:42.680 --> 11:43.960
People still have you.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.120
Zhao.

11:47.720 --> 11:49.000
This is good.

11:50.400 --> 11:51.720
In the court,

11:52.920 --> 11:54.160
you're still fighting.

11:54.800 --> 11:57.120
You care for our people.

12:00.400 --> 12:01.960
Actually, I'm not that selfless.

12:03.040 --> 12:05.880
Initially, I just wanted to stay alive,

12:06.680 --> 12:09.360
but my father died for our people.

12:10.080 --> 12:11.720
As his daughter,

12:11.800 --> 12:13.080
I should strive hard.

12:13.920 --> 12:15.640
I don't know how this will end,

12:15.720 --> 12:17.040
but I'll do my best.

12:21.040 --> 12:21.880
Jiu,

12:21.960 --> 12:25.000
tell me something
about you and Xie Yanfang.

12:30.320 --> 12:31.560
Nothing special.

12:33.120 --> 12:35.120
When I was little, I wasn't accepted.

12:35.640 --> 12:36.960
In a fit of anger,

12:37.040 --> 12:38.720
I burned our ancestral hall.

12:39.240 --> 12:40.920
They would flog me to death.

12:41.760 --> 12:42.800
Xie Yanfang saved me.

12:43.720 --> 12:46.040
He told me I could stay by his side

12:46.120 --> 12:47.280
and one day,

12:48.440 --> 12:50.360
I would become a real member
of that family.

12:51.440 --> 12:52.720
Back then,

12:53.880 --> 12:56.360
I was so eager to be recognized.

12:57.520 --> 12:58.840
So, when I was 16,

12:59.360 --> 13:01.000
he sent me to the Wei Village

13:01.920 --> 13:03.760
to sabotage the trade of Xiaonan caravan.

13:04.600 --> 13:05.480
I did that.

13:06.680 --> 13:07.920
You know what happened next.

13:08.760 --> 13:09.960
Is that why

13:10.640 --> 13:12.680
you were expelled from Xie Family?

13:16.920 --> 13:18.400
I kept heading into the desert

13:20.440 --> 13:21.880
until I met your father.

13:24.600 --> 13:27.880
What about the Bloodburn Pill?

13:29.320 --> 13:32.720
Xie Yanfang gave it to me
before I left home.

13:33.640 --> 13:35.840
He told me the Bloodburn Pill

13:36.680 --> 13:39.720
was a secret elixir
available to our direct line

13:39.800 --> 13:41.440
and could save my life in emergencies.

13:42.360 --> 13:44.120
I had absolute faith in him.

13:44.680 --> 13:46.680
I didn't doubt its function.

13:55.040 --> 13:56.520
Xie Yanfang won't be honest with me.

13:57.560 --> 13:59.320
I'll go to Gaoyang and investigate it.

13:59.400 --> 14:00.920
-Now?
-Yes.

14:03.720 --> 14:04.760
You go back to the Capital.

14:05.360 --> 14:07.640
After I'm done, I'll be back for you.

14:16.360 --> 14:17.320
Wait for me.

14:28.560 --> 14:33.440
‎XIE'S FAMILY HOUSE IN GAOYANG COUNTY

14:36.240 --> 14:38.520
My Lord, the carriages are ready.

14:38.600 --> 14:39.560
We can return anytime.

14:40.160 --> 14:41.200
No hurry.

14:43.520 --> 14:47.080
The Grand Princess accomplished so much

14:48.200 --> 14:49.920
by winning without a battle.

14:50.600 --> 14:52.120
She isn't in a hurry to go back.

14:52.200 --> 14:53.240
Why should we be?

14:53.840 --> 14:55.240
Are you saying…?

14:55.320 --> 14:59.160
We'll go and say congratulations

15:00.640 --> 15:02.000
to Her Highness.

15:08.960 --> 15:11.960
Yanfang, why did you come to Xiaonan?

15:12.960 --> 15:15.600
To thank you for your peerless wisdom

15:16.680 --> 15:19.360
that saved our state from peril.

15:21.280 --> 15:23.360
You flatter me.

15:23.880 --> 15:26.840
It's actually you who saved our state

15:26.920 --> 15:28.800
by taking that urgent mission.

15:29.400 --> 15:32.000
You bravely urged His Majesty
to command the army

15:32.600 --> 15:36.560
against the rebels
even when defamed and denounced.

15:36.640 --> 15:38.320
That deserves the people's praise.

15:38.400 --> 15:41.000
With me leading His Majesty to war,

15:41.080 --> 15:42.480
you overawed the Lord of Xiaonan.

15:43.080 --> 15:46.320
I used you to cut off Xiao Xun's retreat.

15:47.000 --> 15:48.200
We took action far, far away.

15:48.280 --> 15:50.280
But all our steps interlocked.

15:50.360 --> 15:51.920
We cooperated perfectly.

15:52.000 --> 15:55.720
We can truly be called soulmates.

15:56.360 --> 15:57.600
I'm flattered.

15:58.120 --> 16:00.320
After all, your original plan

16:01.080 --> 16:04.320
was to sacrifice my clan
for Xiao Xun's retreat.

16:05.040 --> 16:06.600
That's not right, Your Highness.

16:07.640 --> 16:09.000
Speaking of sacrifice,

16:09.520 --> 16:11.960
when you broke
into Prince of Xiaonan's Residence,

16:12.040 --> 16:14.000
you left me no room

16:14.080 --> 16:16.080
to stop you.

16:16.680 --> 16:18.200
Isn't this just perfect?

16:19.200 --> 16:21.040
We took different actions.

16:21.120 --> 16:22.640
Yet things turned out perfectly.

16:23.360 --> 16:25.360
And I believe you've achieved

16:25.880 --> 16:27.080
what you desired most.

16:28.320 --> 16:30.680
How about I help you a bit more?

16:31.280 --> 16:33.920
I'll delay my return to the Capital.
What do you say?

16:34.520 --> 16:36.160
I'll be happy

16:37.520 --> 16:38.960
if you're back in the Capital.

16:39.840 --> 16:43.840
After all, you're the one and only
to play against me

16:44.360 --> 16:45.600
without losing ground.

16:45.680 --> 16:47.520
If you aren't in the Capital,

16:49.000 --> 16:50.680
won't that be boring?

16:51.280 --> 16:52.840
But anyway, you're right.

16:52.920 --> 16:54.800
I do owe you something.

16:55.440 --> 16:57.680
Yu has grown a bit closer to me.

16:57.760 --> 16:59.320
As his uncle,

17:00.000 --> 17:01.480
I feel quite relieved.

17:02.120 --> 17:03.840
I told you.

17:04.359 --> 17:06.720
Family bonds aren't so easy to sever.

17:07.280 --> 17:09.119
It's time you got closer.

17:09.720 --> 17:12.280
You've earned all this
by doing good deeds.

17:12.359 --> 17:13.400
I don't deserve the credit.

17:14.920 --> 17:18.400
I wonder when you will
return to the Capital.

17:19.079 --> 17:21.880
Xiao Xun devastated the people
all along the way.

17:22.400 --> 17:24.040
And it is now the farming season.

17:24.640 --> 17:26.800
I'll make an inspection tour
to reassure people

17:26.880 --> 17:28.280
on His Majesty's behalf.

17:31.440 --> 17:33.000
With you around,

17:33.520 --> 17:35.360
everything will be alright.

17:35.440 --> 17:37.360
And thank you for easing
the people's burdens.

17:38.000 --> 17:39.320
Otherwise, at this moment,

17:39.400 --> 17:41.080
how could I be sitting here at ease?

17:42.320 --> 17:45.000
Even the redwood forest before my eyes

17:45.080 --> 17:47.080
would have been burned down in the war.

17:48.040 --> 17:49.600
So, I've been waiting here

17:49.680 --> 17:50.640
to make this toast

17:50.720 --> 17:52.360
with tea instead of wine

17:52.880 --> 17:54.320
for the sake of our people.

18:04.520 --> 18:05.960
The second toast

18:07.920 --> 18:09.520
is to offer my apology.

18:10.200 --> 18:13.280
I revealed your uncle's dealings
with Xiao Xun

18:13.360 --> 18:15.680
because I didn't have a choice.

18:17.760 --> 18:19.080
I know.

18:19.160 --> 18:21.120
If the court hadn't hunted my uncle,

18:21.720 --> 18:24.400
they wouldn't have approached
Xiao Xun so smoothly.

18:24.480 --> 18:27.400
What you did benefited both of us.

18:29.000 --> 18:30.240
You don't mind

18:30.880 --> 18:32.920
only because you're broad-minded.

18:35.480 --> 18:37.840
I wonder if you like mountain climbing.

18:38.600 --> 18:40.520
Have a try when possible.

18:41.440 --> 18:42.880
I believe you'll like it.

18:43.880 --> 18:46.000
When you stand on the summit

18:46.600 --> 18:48.560
and gaze upon everything,

18:49.560 --> 18:50.920
you will know the feeling

18:51.880 --> 18:53.840
of wandering freely across the land.

18:54.440 --> 18:56.040
So what you want

18:56.120 --> 18:58.320
is to reign over the masses

18:58.400 --> 19:00.400
and take everything under control?

19:00.480 --> 19:01.760
To be honest,

19:03.000 --> 19:05.760
when I knew the Lord of Xiaonan
rose up in rebellion,

19:05.840 --> 19:07.280
I was really delighted.

19:07.360 --> 19:09.640
I finally had an opportunity

19:10.840 --> 19:12.440
to make up for my regret.

19:13.120 --> 19:16.520
But sadly, I disrupted that.

19:17.840 --> 19:18.960
Should I

19:20.920 --> 19:24.520
make the third toast to apologize to you?

19:25.280 --> 19:26.840
For the state and the people,

19:28.000 --> 19:29.200
you did nothing wrong.

19:29.720 --> 19:31.800
You don't have to apologize to anyone.

19:33.320 --> 19:36.040
I'm quite relieved to hear you say that.

19:40.240 --> 19:41.720
But I'm quite curious.

19:42.520 --> 19:44.480
Why did you take that risk yourself?

19:45.360 --> 19:47.360
It's all right that you don't trust me.

19:48.160 --> 19:50.920
But you must trust my determination
to kill Lord of Xiaonan for His Majesty.

19:51.720 --> 19:54.440
You would rather die
with the Lord of Xiaonan

19:54.520 --> 19:55.880
than discuss it with me.

19:55.960 --> 19:57.720
Do you find me

19:58.640 --> 20:00.560
even more terrifying?

20:05.080 --> 20:06.480
Yanfang,

20:07.480 --> 20:09.080
you were fighting for yourself

20:10.040 --> 20:11.240
while I was fighting for myself.

20:12.080 --> 20:14.240
I didn't want to disrupt your plan.

20:14.840 --> 20:18.240
Nor could I let you plan for me.

20:19.400 --> 20:20.480
Fine.

20:21.640 --> 20:23.040
You and I fight our own war.

20:23.640 --> 20:25.040
When we share the same goal,

20:26.000 --> 20:28.280
we're fighting side by side too.

20:31.400 --> 20:32.240
What about Xie Yanlai?

20:33.720 --> 20:36.960
Have you thought about fighting
side by side with him?

20:40.440 --> 20:41.720
Your Highness,

20:43.600 --> 20:44.640
why do you ask?

20:46.160 --> 20:47.480
Nothing.

20:48.520 --> 20:49.840
I simply want to know

20:50.520 --> 20:53.760
what you think of your brother.

20:54.440 --> 20:55.840
Like you said,

20:56.360 --> 20:57.680
he's my brother.

20:58.360 --> 20:59.640
How could I do him harm?

20:59.720 --> 21:02.800
Besides, Yanlai grew up by my side.

21:02.880 --> 21:04.920
I know him better than anyone.

21:05.000 --> 21:07.200
Since he chose to follow you,

21:07.720 --> 21:09.320
he would never betray you.

21:10.520 --> 21:12.080
Did you ask that

21:12.920 --> 21:14.720
because you didn't fully trust him

21:16.880 --> 21:18.720
or because he was one of my family?

21:21.200 --> 21:24.400
Thank you for the tea. I must get going.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.560
Yu is waiting for you.

21:29.640 --> 21:30.680
Go back early.

21:33.080 --> 21:36.800
This time, you didn't kill
the Lord of Xiaonan with your own blade,

21:37.400 --> 21:38.840
but I believe

21:38.920 --> 21:41.800
you will find a way to cut off his allies

21:41.880 --> 21:42.920
and crush his sinews.

21:48.280 --> 21:50.360
Even if he were a mountain,

21:50.440 --> 21:53.040
you would be able
to flatten him with your bare hands.

21:58.720 --> 21:59.720
That's right.

22:01.240 --> 22:02.520
I would.

22:05.080 --> 22:06.520
Wait a minute.

22:13.480 --> 22:14.960
Take this back.

22:20.280 --> 22:22.840
Thank you for keeping it for me.

22:23.520 --> 22:25.400
Glad you trusted me.

22:26.560 --> 22:29.120
Du Qi, see Her Highness off.

22:29.200 --> 22:30.120
Yes.

22:50.800 --> 22:51.920
Mr. Xie,

22:52.000 --> 22:54.120
she is intentionally going against you.

22:55.120 --> 22:56.800
She's just being herself.

22:58.400 --> 23:00.200
She serves no one.

23:01.960 --> 23:04.720
Whatever happens,
she naturally puts herself first.

23:05.560 --> 23:07.720
She isn't on our side.

23:09.360 --> 23:11.720
We aren't on her side either.

23:14.440 --> 23:16.400
She and I are just alike.

23:17.000 --> 23:18.360
She takes very few guards now.

23:18.960 --> 23:20.840
-Shall we just…
-Du Qi,

23:23.520 --> 23:25.920
Yu relies on Chu Zhao.

23:26.000 --> 23:27.760
She can be killed by anyone,

23:28.520 --> 23:31.000
anyone but my clan.

23:33.280 --> 23:34.160
I got it.

23:34.920 --> 23:36.000
Anyway,

23:39.280 --> 23:41.960
it's not about how hard it is.

23:44.760 --> 23:46.040
Then what is it about?

23:49.840 --> 23:53.320
I've finally met a true match.

23:57.280 --> 23:58.800
How could I bear to kill her?

24:01.000 --> 24:03.240
CHU MANSION

24:03.320 --> 24:05.880
Father. Mother. Zhao is here.

24:05.960 --> 24:07.160
Be right there. Hurry.

24:08.000 --> 24:09.240
Zhao.

24:09.320 --> 24:10.520
-Zhao.
-Oh, Zhao.

24:10.600 --> 24:11.880
-Zhao.
-Zhao.

24:11.960 --> 24:13.480
Sorry, I was so foolish.

24:13.560 --> 24:15.640
I just was.

24:15.720 --> 24:18.160
Deceived by Xiao Xun,
we nearly got you in trouble.

24:18.240 --> 24:19.360
That's right.

24:19.440 --> 24:20.880
What's gone is gone.

24:21.560 --> 24:22.680
When you're alive,

24:22.760 --> 24:24.800
my father would be relieved,
even in the underworld.

24:25.920 --> 24:26.960
That's right.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.440
Tang,

24:29.520 --> 24:31.440
I have a mission for you.

24:32.960 --> 24:34.040
Mission again?

24:34.560 --> 24:35.640
But I…

24:35.720 --> 24:38.560
Will it be another mission
that may get me killed?

24:40.120 --> 24:42.880
I want you to hold
a literary gathering for me.

24:45.240 --> 24:46.280
Now?

24:47.120 --> 24:49.320
But the Capital is in turmoil.

24:50.080 --> 24:53.280
All the clans are observing. What if…?

24:53.360 --> 24:54.400
That's why.

24:56.160 --> 24:57.440
Mr. Zhou loves cranes.

24:57.520 --> 24:59.040
The head of the Qi Family loves swords.

24:59.120 --> 25:00.200
The Pei ladies excel at guqin.

25:01.040 --> 25:02.240
You know who to invite.

25:03.280 --> 25:04.120
But I… I…

25:04.200 --> 25:06.560
These people secure the state.

25:06.640 --> 25:09.160
We can't stabilize the court
without their support.

25:10.760 --> 25:13.280
Jiu followed me
to the Prince of Xiaonan's Mansion.

25:13.360 --> 25:15.200
Lord of Xiaonan was wary of him

25:15.280 --> 25:17.280
simply because he came
from the Xie Family.

25:17.800 --> 25:20.160
This century-old family
is the pillar of our state.

25:20.240 --> 25:23.520
Xie Yanfang knows the Zhou Family
helped you escape

25:23.600 --> 25:25.520
but doesn't dare to give them a hard time

25:25.600 --> 25:27.960
because they've been loyal
with great prestige.

25:29.400 --> 25:31.440
Big clans are the foundation of court.

25:31.520 --> 25:32.840
To govern a state,

25:32.920 --> 25:35.520
the ministers must be united
and help each other.

25:35.600 --> 25:37.760
Do you understand the meaning?

25:37.840 --> 25:40.160
Zhao, you've changed.

25:41.440 --> 25:42.520
No.

25:43.280 --> 25:44.480
I just

25:44.560 --> 25:47.400
have learned to play by their rules.

25:48.320 --> 25:50.320
TAIJI HALL

25:50.400 --> 25:51.320
By the way,

25:51.400 --> 25:54.000
what has the Grand Mentor
been doing lately?

25:54.080 --> 25:56.320
Made a fortune again?
Going over the accounts?

25:56.400 --> 25:57.720
Lord of Xiaonan…

25:58.240 --> 26:00.840
Oh no. Prince of State.

26:00.920 --> 26:02.720
He must have got a lot from His Lordship.

26:03.440 --> 26:06.280
Maybe he even

26:06.360 --> 26:09.680
got his position in the same way.

26:09.760 --> 26:10.920
In that case,

26:11.000 --> 26:12.920
His Lordship is still

26:13.440 --> 26:15.240
controlling the court.

26:17.040 --> 26:18.360
His Majesty is here.

26:18.440 --> 26:20.160
So is Young Master Xie Yanfang.

26:20.240 --> 26:23.200
Deng Yi won't seize all power for himself.

26:23.280 --> 26:26.840
Today, my daughter got up even earlier
than I came to court.

26:26.920 --> 26:29.200
I didn't even see her at breakfast.

26:29.280 --> 26:31.200
I was told she went off
to do something big.

26:31.280 --> 26:33.640
Recently, all the ladies have been busy.

26:33.720 --> 26:36.240
What's more, they've been spending a lot.

26:37.560 --> 26:39.920
Is the Grand Princess coming back?

26:40.800 --> 26:42.880
Her Highness is at the height of her fame.

26:43.480 --> 26:45.440
If she intends to return,

26:45.520 --> 26:48.160
we should prepare in advance
to welcome her.

26:48.240 --> 26:51.080
Ladies in my family
clamor to imitate Her Highness.

26:51.160 --> 26:53.120
They come out from the inner chambers.

26:56.080 --> 26:58.040
It's late. Why hasn't
His Majesty come yet?

26:58.120 --> 27:00.280
His Majesty is slacking off for once.

27:00.360 --> 27:02.880
After the New Year, he's one year older.

27:03.400 --> 27:04.880
But he's less diligent.

27:06.520 --> 27:09.080
His Majesty isn't slacking off.

27:50.800 --> 27:54.280
Greetings, Your Majesty.
Greetings, Your Highness.

27:57.640 --> 27:59.520
Rise, all of you.

28:00.040 --> 28:01.920
Thank you, Your Majesty.

28:03.080 --> 28:04.520
I was away for a long time.

28:05.120 --> 28:06.400
When I'm back here,

28:06.480 --> 28:09.160
I see all of you
still work hard on state affairs.

28:09.680 --> 28:10.880
I'm quite relieved.

28:11.880 --> 28:13.160
Your Highness,

28:13.240 --> 28:15.640
you made great merit in pacifying

28:15.720 --> 28:17.040
the Northern Desert riot.

28:17.640 --> 28:19.520
-We…
-You flatter me.

28:19.600 --> 28:21.120
It's the duty

28:21.200 --> 28:23.680
of our Chu Clan to protect the state.

28:24.840 --> 28:26.600
But when I was away,

28:27.560 --> 28:30.080
I heard a lot of criticism.

28:30.680 --> 28:32.520
‎Well…

28:32.600 --> 28:33.840
Today,

28:33.920 --> 28:37.000
I'll make everything clear
before all of you.

28:37.640 --> 28:41.680
I do everything just to assist His Majesty

28:42.280 --> 28:44.320
and keep our state secure for all ages.

28:44.960 --> 28:46.560
When the late Emperor entrusted me,

28:47.080 --> 28:49.480
he knew I wasn't someone
to be locked in the inner palace.

28:50.080 --> 28:51.000
In the future,

28:51.600 --> 28:53.400
I never want to hear

28:53.480 --> 28:55.920
any gossip about me
interfering with politics.

29:09.920 --> 29:11.240
At tomorrow's court,

29:11.760 --> 29:13.320
I want you to detail your methods

29:13.400 --> 29:15.560
of frontier farming
and people's reassurance.

29:16.720 --> 29:19.360
Ministers, if you find it
stifling indoors,

29:19.440 --> 29:23.240
why don't you move out of the hall?

29:23.320 --> 29:25.680
Having the court in the sunlight

29:25.760 --> 29:27.280
may make you feel more refreshed.

29:31.360 --> 29:32.520
After all,

29:33.160 --> 29:34.800
governing a state is like traveling.

29:36.440 --> 29:38.880
We have to see what lies ahead

29:38.960 --> 29:40.520
to avoid going off track.

29:48.240 --> 29:52.080
‎WISDOM AND VIRTUES

30:12.440 --> 30:14.520
I came back too hastily,

30:15.040 --> 30:16.080
and the frontier is poor.

30:16.720 --> 30:19.480
I didn't prepare gifts for you, Mr. Deng.

30:20.000 --> 30:21.280
Please forgive my rudeness.

30:21.360 --> 30:22.720
Don't say that.

30:22.800 --> 30:24.680
Your Highness put down
the Xiaonan rebellion

30:24.760 --> 30:25.880
and saved your uncle's family.

30:25.960 --> 30:28.200
You were really courageous.

30:28.920 --> 30:31.280
Seeing you sit here safe and sound

30:31.880 --> 30:33.520
is the greatest gift to me.

30:34.760 --> 30:35.920
Thank you for your concern.

30:40.120 --> 30:42.120
After this journey,

30:42.200 --> 30:43.720
Your Highness has totally changed.

30:44.600 --> 30:45.960
What you said in the court today

30:47.680 --> 30:49.880
intimidated everyone.

30:54.840 --> 30:59.080
Anyway, I couldn't make it back
without your help.

30:59.680 --> 31:02.680
I'll make this toast to express my thanks.

31:03.320 --> 31:05.160
Compared to Mr. Xie's tea,

31:05.240 --> 31:07.280
the tea I'm offering

31:08.200 --> 31:10.320
might be rather bland.

31:10.400 --> 31:11.280
I just hope

31:11.360 --> 31:14.000
you won't blame me for my risky move.

31:14.080 --> 31:16.080
That's what I think too.

31:17.240 --> 31:19.240
If you have any further plans,

31:20.160 --> 31:21.240
please tell me in advance.

31:21.840 --> 31:23.560
If you move so unexpectedly again,

31:23.640 --> 31:26.080
you and I might end up falling out.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.960
If I had informed you,

31:28.480 --> 31:30.200
would you approve?

31:32.920 --> 31:34.280
No.

31:34.360 --> 31:36.000
You would stop me.

31:36.520 --> 31:38.040
In that case,

31:38.560 --> 31:40.560
our mutual trust would also be harmed.

31:44.280 --> 31:45.560
You are right to rebuke me.

31:47.800 --> 31:49.840
I'm to blame for the discord

31:49.920 --> 31:51.520
between His Majesty and ministers.

31:52.800 --> 31:54.840
His Majesty is innocent.

31:55.440 --> 31:56.800
Lately,

31:56.880 --> 31:58.480
have you kept an eye on Xiaonan?

31:58.560 --> 32:00.880
Are you interested in Xiaonan

32:00.960 --> 32:03.480
or the Xie Family's soldiers
around Xiaonan?

32:03.560 --> 32:04.880
Xiaonan is no longer a threat.

32:04.960 --> 32:06.160
When we focused

32:06.240 --> 32:09.280
on Xiaonan and the Northern Desert,

32:09.360 --> 32:10.720
we didn't see the Xie Family

32:10.800 --> 32:12.760
place many followers
without being noticed.

32:13.640 --> 32:14.840
Mr. Deng,

32:14.920 --> 32:18.240
what do you think they're doing this for?

32:18.320 --> 32:21.560
You and I know it very well.

32:23.960 --> 32:26.920
If the game board becomes unbalanced,

32:27.520 --> 32:29.040
someone has to balance it.

32:29.120 --> 32:30.720
Are you saying

32:30.800 --> 32:34.320
you want me to balance it?

32:36.480 --> 32:38.600
The balance lies in equal power.

32:39.120 --> 32:41.280
The Xie Family is too powerful
to be underestimated.

32:42.680 --> 32:46.080
Mr. Deng, you aim for a high position.

32:46.160 --> 32:47.000
Why?

32:47.080 --> 32:48.880
The same reason as yours.

32:49.480 --> 32:50.760
I want no one

32:51.960 --> 32:54.080
to stand in my way anymore.

32:55.120 --> 32:56.440
In that case,

32:56.960 --> 32:58.560
why do you bother with leadership?

32:59.520 --> 33:01.760
You and I are on the same path.

33:02.400 --> 33:05.160
We will also do the same thing.

33:05.880 --> 33:08.840
Then why don't we join forces?

33:14.240 --> 33:19.480
‎GAOYANG COUNTY

34:22.600 --> 34:23.880
You're here again.

34:23.960 --> 34:26.560
Yes. I came to congratulate you.

34:27.880 --> 34:29.000
On what?

34:29.800 --> 34:31.880
You said something to Chu Tang

34:31.960 --> 34:34.199
about the clans you would win over.

34:34.960 --> 34:37.000
It means you've realized

34:37.080 --> 34:38.920
what matters most.

34:39.920 --> 34:41.840
Now you should think carefully

34:41.920 --> 34:45.719
about what you should give up.

34:46.320 --> 34:47.480
Give up?

34:47.560 --> 34:49.159
Give up Xie Yanlai

34:49.239 --> 34:51.280
and choose Xie Yanfang.

34:51.360 --> 34:54.360
Then your path to power will be steadier

34:54.440 --> 34:55.440
and smoother.

34:59.640 --> 35:00.680
No.

35:00.760 --> 35:02.040
Why are you being foolish again?

35:02.760 --> 35:04.480
What's so good about Xie Yanlai?

35:04.560 --> 35:05.640
He has great martial arts,

35:05.720 --> 35:07.600
but can he fight off an army?

35:07.680 --> 35:10.360
Can he withstand the dispute in the court?

35:13.360 --> 35:14.440
Jiu

35:15.360 --> 35:16.320
is sincere with me.

35:16.400 --> 35:17.480
Sincere?

35:17.560 --> 35:20.760
In front of power,
sincerity is the least valuable.

35:21.360 --> 35:24.320
Xie Yanfang is the true master
of his clan.

35:24.400 --> 35:28.200
He's worth ten times more than Xie Yanlai.

35:29.200 --> 35:30.880
Don't you understand?

35:30.960 --> 35:32.080
To live well,

35:32.160 --> 35:35.760
you must be more ruthless
and scheming than them.

35:36.800 --> 35:38.920
Xie Yanfang wants an ally, doesn't he?

35:39.000 --> 35:40.760
Then give him one.

35:41.800 --> 35:45.040
Let him think he can truly control you.

35:45.640 --> 35:48.120
Little does he know a hunter

35:48.640 --> 35:51.280
often appears in the guise of the prey.

35:53.080 --> 35:54.040
Zhao.

35:54.920 --> 35:55.840
Zhao.

35:56.360 --> 35:57.480
Zhao.

35:58.600 --> 36:00.280
Play on the swing with me.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.880
Zhao,

36:22.960 --> 36:24.320
what's wrong?

36:24.920 --> 36:25.920
Nothing.

36:26.440 --> 36:27.560
I'm just

36:29.040 --> 36:30.640
missing my mother.

36:32.280 --> 36:33.640
Actually,

36:33.720 --> 36:36.520
I also wish my parents could be alive.

36:37.120 --> 36:38.560
That would be enough.

36:39.080 --> 36:41.520
Even if Father still didn't play with me…

36:42.600 --> 36:45.440
Even if Mother still lectured me…

36:47.080 --> 36:48.560
But in this life,

36:49.240 --> 36:50.800
nothing can be perfect.

36:52.320 --> 36:53.880
Just like my mother.

36:54.960 --> 36:57.120
I didn't have a good talk with her.

36:58.920 --> 37:01.200
I got no chance to call her Mother.

37:02.080 --> 37:05.320
Then she died in the battle
to save my life.

37:06.880 --> 37:08.160
I didn't even

37:10.920 --> 37:13.680
truly remember what she looked like.

37:14.640 --> 37:15.680
The same with me.

37:16.520 --> 37:18.080
As time goes by,

37:18.600 --> 37:22.240
my mother's face
grows fainter in my dreams.

37:23.960 --> 37:25.560
According to Uncle Yanfang,

37:25.640 --> 37:27.120
it's because I'm growing up.

37:28.120 --> 37:32.800
But why does that make me
forget my mother's face?

37:33.320 --> 37:34.880
I don't want to forget.

37:36.400 --> 37:37.800
To forget

37:39.640 --> 37:42.200
might be a protection from our mothers.

37:43.400 --> 37:45.400
But Uncle Yanfang
came up with an idea for me.

37:45.480 --> 37:47.200
What was that?

37:47.280 --> 37:50.320
Uncle Yanfang
told me stories about Mother.

37:50.400 --> 37:51.760
He also painted a portrait of her

37:51.840 --> 37:53.600
and hung it in my room.

37:53.680 --> 37:55.120
Then, I wouldn't forget her.

37:55.720 --> 37:58.080
But… But sadly,

37:58.600 --> 38:01.120
the wind blew it down a few days ago,

38:01.200 --> 38:02.960
and it was stained.

38:10.600 --> 38:12.920
Actually, forgetting her face
won't be a problem.

38:15.280 --> 38:18.560
As long as you remember
the warmth of her embrace

38:20.360 --> 38:22.280
and the rhymes she hummed for you,

38:23.840 --> 38:25.480
she will always stay in your heart

38:26.480 --> 38:27.800
and never be forgotten.

38:29.840 --> 38:31.520
Uncle Yanfang said the same thing.

38:34.720 --> 38:37.680
Now, you seem to like Uncle Yanfang a lot.

38:38.880 --> 38:40.120
He's been nice to me.

38:40.640 --> 38:42.880
Last time, he took me to the war.

38:43.640 --> 38:45.240
He even tried the armor on me.

38:45.840 --> 38:47.360
I looked so cool.

38:58.280 --> 38:59.360
Zhao,

38:59.440 --> 39:01.960
from now on, I'm your family.

39:02.040 --> 39:04.440
The closest one. All right?

39:08.640 --> 39:09.640
Sure.

39:13.120 --> 39:16.000
But Yu, nothing in life is certain.

39:16.880 --> 39:18.720
You must grow up quickly.

39:19.240 --> 39:21.080
Become a mature man.

39:22.320 --> 39:23.480
In that case,

39:24.440 --> 39:27.480
even if one day, I'm not by your side,

39:29.080 --> 39:31.000
you can be your own support

39:32.160 --> 39:33.600
and the backbone of the people.

39:36.400 --> 39:37.680
I will.

39:37.760 --> 39:39.760
I will be as strong as you.

39:39.840 --> 39:41.400
I will be a good emperor.

40:27.200 --> 40:29.280
-Open it.
-Young Master,

40:29.360 --> 40:31.680
how could you be so presumptuous?

40:31.760 --> 40:33.960
If the clan head knows,

40:34.040 --> 40:37.040
I'm afraid I'll lose my life.

40:37.760 --> 40:40.160
Do you want to lose your life

40:41.120 --> 40:42.560
when Xie Yanfang knows?

40:44.040 --> 40:45.200
Or do you want me

40:47.520 --> 40:48.760
to kill you right now?

40:59.200 --> 41:00.040
MEDICINAL CYATHULA ROOT

41:36.360 --> 41:39.240
What are these elixirs for?

41:39.880 --> 41:40.720
Young Master,

41:40.800 --> 41:43.480
they're for preserving someone's life.

41:44.640 --> 41:46.760
-Whose life?
-I…

41:46.840 --> 41:48.280
I don't know.

42:00.320 --> 42:02.120
I really don't know.

42:03.000 --> 42:05.920
All I know is since five years ago,

42:06.000 --> 42:08.040
the clan head has had them delivered

42:08.120 --> 42:09.880
every three months.

42:09.960 --> 42:12.720
Yet no one but Du Qi

42:12.800 --> 42:14.640
would know who actually

42:14.720 --> 42:17.000
needs these elixirs.

42:17.520 --> 42:18.920
Five years ago?

42:19.480 --> 42:21.720
Yes. That was when you…

42:22.800 --> 42:26.760
You were involved in the fire case
of the Wei Village.

42:46.560 --> 42:47.560
Xiang.
